<!-- 3. AOI STATE MACHINE -->
<div class="card" id="sec-aoi">
<h2 style="color:var(--g);font-size:15px">3. SKT_AOI_TCP_SERVER — State Machine</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>State</th><th>Action</th><th>Next</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">0</td><td>Initialize — copy MSG paths, set timeouts</td><td class="mo">10</td><td>On Enable_Socket rising edge</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">10</td><td>Socket Create (MSG)</td><td class="mo">15</td><td>Creates TCP socket instance</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">15</td><td>Check Create result</td><td class="mo">20/110</td><td>Error → cleanup</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">20</td><td>Socket Accept — listen for ProPlanner</td><td class="mo">25</td><td>PLC waits for client</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">25</td><td>Check Accept result</td><td class="mo">40/20/100</td><td style="color:var(--ob)">ERR=0xFF/EXERR=0x46 = timeout → retry. Normal.</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">40</td><td>Client connected — setup R/W instances</td><td class="mo">50</td><td>Accept_Response has client instance</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo" style="color:var(--gb);font-weight:700">50</td><td style="color:var(--gb)"><strong>READ LOOP — check for data</strong></td><td class="mo">55/60</td><td style="color:var(--gb)">Main operating state</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">55</td><td>Process read — set READ flag if data</td><td class="mo">60</td><td>READ=1 when Buffer.LEN > 0</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo" style="color:var(--ob);font-weight:700">60</td><td style="color:var(--ob)"><strong>WRITE CHECK — send response</strong></td><td class="mo">65/70</td><td>Buffer loaded before WRITE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">65</td><td>Process write result</td><td class="mo">70</td><td>WRITE unlatched after send</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">70</td><td>Loop — enabled → 50, disabled → 100</td><td class="mo">50/100</td><td>Continuous R/W loop</td></tr>
<tr><td class="mo">100-110</td><td>Cleanup — delete socket, reset</td><td class="mo">0</td><td>Auto-restarts if Enable TRUE</td></tr>
</table>

