<!-- 4. REFERENCE CODE -->
<div class="card i" id="sec-ref">
<h2 style="color:var(--g);font-size:15px">4. Reference Code Analysis — Rands650562</h2>
<p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--ts);margin-bottom:8px">From CNH reference implementation on 5069-L306ER. Cognex IS3800 + analog distance measurement.</p>

<h3 style="color:var(--ob);font-size:12px">Inbound Message Parsing</h3>
<div class="rc">// ProPlanner sends ASCII string → PLC parses with MID()
MID(LastRead, 1, 4, StepString);    // 1 char at pos 4
STOD(StepString, StepNum);           // → INT

// StepNum: 1=Abort, 2=Camera Job, 3=Camera Trigger, 4=Press Check

// Camera Job (StepNum=2):
MID(LastRead, 4, 6, CameraJobString); // 4 chars at pos 6
STOD(CameraJobString, CameraJob);

// Press/Distance (StepNum=4):
MID(LastRead, 5, 5, DistanceString);     // 5 chars at pos 5
DesiredDistance := DistanceDint / 1000;
MID(LastRead, 6, 11, ToleranceString);   // 6 chars at pos 11
Tolerance := ToleranceDint / 1000;
MID(LastRead, 6, 15, PressStepNum);      // 6 chars at pos 15
MaxDistance := DesiredDistance + Tolerance;
MinDistance := DesiredDistance - Tolerance;</div>

<h3 style="color:var(--ob);font-size:12px;margin-top:10px">Outbound Response Building</h3>
<div class="rc">// PASS:
CONCAT(PressHeader, Pass, Message);       // "PRESS;PASS;"
CONCAT(Message, ReachedString, Message);  // Append distance
CONCAT(Message, semicol, Message);
CONCAT(Message, PressStepNum, Message);

// FAIL (too short):
CONCAT(PressHeader, Fail, Message);       // "PRESS;FAIL;"
CONCAT(Message, PressToShort, Message);   // "SHORT;"

// Camera:
IF (IS3800:I.InspectionResults[0] = 1) THEN
    Message := PicPass;                   // "PIC;PASS;"
END_IF;

// Trigger write:
IF (JobChanged OR Triggered OR PressComplete) THEN
    Write_Data_Server := 1;
END_IF;</div>

<div class="nt2"><strong>Key Takeaway:</strong> ASCII command in → MID() parse → execute → CONCAT() response → socket write. No binary, no CRC. AOI handles TCP lifecycle.</div>
</div>

