<!-- 5. PROTOCOL -->
<div class="card" id="sec-proto">
<h2 style="color:var(--g);font-size:15px">5. ASCII String Protocol</h2>
<h3 style="color:var(--ob);font-size:12px">Inbound (ProPlanner → PLC)</h3>
<div class="mb">Position:  1234|5...|...........|...............
           SSSS DDDDD DDDDDDDDDDD DDDDDDDDDDDDDD
           └──┘ └───────────────────────────────┘
           Step    Variable payload (step-dependent)

StepNum: Position 4, Length 1
  MID(LastRead, 1, 4, StepString) → STOD → StepNum</div>

<h3 style="color:var(--ob);font-size:12px;margin-top:10px">Outbound (PLC → ProPlanner)</h3>
<div class="mb">Built via CONCAT(), semicolon-delimited:
  Press Pass:   "PRESS;PASS;12345;000004;"
  Press Fail:   "PRESS;FAIL;SHORT;12345;000004;"
  Vision Pass:  "PIC;PASS;"
  Vision Fail:  "PIC;FAIL;"
  Job Changed:  "JOB;COMPLETE;"
  Camera Off:   "CAM;OFFLINE;"</div>
</div>

