<p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--ts);margin-bottom:8px">MWES creates recipe managers on OPTIX. Operators enter pass/fail criteria. PLC tests real-time. No storage.</p>
<div class="g2">
<div>
<h3 style="color:var(--g);font-size:12px">Operator Enters on OPTIX</h3>
<table><tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Example</th></tr>
<tr><td>Recipe Name</td><td>STRING</td><td class="mo">"S18_BRG_PRESS"</td></tr>
<tr><td>Target Distance</td><td>REAL (mm)</td><td class="mo">25.400</td></tr>
<tr><td>Tolerance</td><td>REAL (mm)</td><td class="mo">0.050</td></tr>
<tr><td>Max Force</td><td>REAL (N)</td><td class="mo">27500.0</td></tr>
